<h2>New Task Assigned</h2>

<div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0;">
    <h3>{{name}}</h3>
    <p><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{due_date}}</p>
    <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
</div>

<p>Hello {{assigned_user_name}},</p>

<p>You have been assigned a new task in WondrlabApp:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Task:</strong> {{name}}</li>
    {{#if opportunity_name}}
    <li><strong>Opportunity:</strong> {{opportunity_name}}</li>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if client_name}}
    <li><strong>Client:</strong> {{client_name}}</li>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if service_name}}
    <li><strong>Service:</strong> {{service_name}}</li>
    {{/if}}
    <li><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{due_date}}</li>
    {{#if description}}
    <li><strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}</li>
    {{/if}}
</ul>

<p>Please log into WondrlabApp to view the full task details and begin working on it.</p>

<a href="{{app_url}}/tasks" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #3498db; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;">View Task</a>

<p>If you have any questions about this task, please contact your supervisor or the task creator.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
WondrlabApp Team</p>